    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy and is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been perfectly preserved and is ready to hit the road, this is it. Drop me a message, I'd love to tell you more!",
