    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system for optimal torque across the rev range. This example utilizes the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, paired with a speed-sensitive variable M-differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, with no signs of subframe stress, and retains factory-spec suspension kinematics for surgical handling. Every mechanical component, from the ventilated rotors to the bushings, reflects a vehicle kept in a climate-controlled environment. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
