    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Every body panel is original, with factory-perfect gaps and not a single stone chip or door ding to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing or wear, and the original factory protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, it is flawless. It has been serviced exclusively at the authorized dealership with a comprehensive paper trail documenting every scheduled maintenance and inspection. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a turn-key masterpiece that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
