    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is a total dream\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, keeping it spotless inside and out. It\u2019s been babied its whole life, always garage-kept, and you won't find a single blemish on it. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love how smooth it is!",
